QuestData.Title: Meet with Tamanji
QuestData.Description: I received a scroll for you from Tamanji in Orgrimmar. She wants you to make your way to The Barracks in the Valley of Honor and speak with her as soon as you can. It sounded urgent, $n.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Tamanji at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Tamanji at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
